column11:
  This note sharpens the standard upper bound of the least quadratic nonresidue
from $n_p\ll p^{1/4\sqrt{e}+\varepsilon}$ to $n_p\ll p^{1/4e+\varepsilon}$,
where $\varepsilon>0$, unconditionally.
